Name: Strong Molding Agent
Description: A required additive for refining finished gems.
Description$english: A required additive for refining finished gems.
Description2$english: The Artisan Guild was dissatisfied with the market's stereotype of the Molding Agent, so they launched an improved version - it is said to facilitate polishing, aid in shaping, and improve purification rates. However, its overly fragrant smell and overly soft texture led to even more rumors in the market, and even an improved version was launched in response to the times.
